{"tid":130212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自稱被困屯門山頭多天　直昇機吊熱褲紋身女送院","createTime":"2017-02-22T08:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T08:55:02.000Z","uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"959ce5fd39d7a4251f671988714e62014cd308dd","tid":130212,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/441293/xlarge/b364881fba95b9380d35fab3fb1b33df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F441293%2Fxlarge%2Fb364881fba95b9380d35fab3fb1b33df.jpg&h=d013309a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/441269/xlarge/bd1699964d4edc7750267a08eeac348f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F441269%2Fxlarge%2Fbd1699964d4edc7750267a08eeac348f.jpg&h=31b54388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，數名行山人士在屯門良景村對上山頭遠足，途至麒麟圍對開山頭時，發現一名中年女子在山澗附近受傷，立即趨近了解，所幸仍然清醒有知覺，代為報警求救。<br />\n<br />\n大批救援人員接報到場，包括消防、救護及警員，在山腳集合登山營救，花約1小時尋獲該名傷者，救護員立即為傷者作初步治理。疑因上址崎嶇，救援人員隨後召政府飛行服務隊直升機到場協助，吊起傷者送往就近的屯門醫院治理。消息稱，有人事後報稱自己被困山頭10多天。警方正調查傷者身份及事發經過，初步列作「行山人士求警協助」跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/441278/xlarge/a86cccd850df5a60f20cab939de04d1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F441278%2Fxlarge%2Fa86cccd850df5a60f20cab939de04d1c.jpg&h=7197c7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/73653/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F73653%2F&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=57661a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/73653/</a>"},{"pid":"5e24b168df4050adb2eedc8b40595e59cc8cb59e","tid":130212,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"中年女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02beff81c86b4eb18d8f352ed181cdd4fe8043","tid":130212,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"是不是覺得此題怪怪的?!此題疑點很多, 整個劇情是可以推出來的~自己在題中找找線索~"}]}